{"title":{"en":"A. Suffix Array - 2","ru":"A. Суффиксный массив - 2"},"contestId":"269103","problemIndex":"A","timeLimit":{"en":"2 seconds","ru":"2 секунды"},"memLimit":{"en":"512 megabytes","ru":"512 мегабайт"},"inputFormat":{"en":"standard input","ru":"стандартный ввод"},"outputFormat":{"en":"standard output","ru":"стандартный вывод"},"problemHtml":{"en":"<p>This task is the same as the previous one, but the length of string is larger. Try to write as efficient an algorithm as possible.</p><p>Build a suffix array for the given string $$$s$$$.</p>","ru":"<p>Эта задача такая же, как предыдущая, но ограничения немного больше. Попробуйте написать по возможности эффективный алгоритм.</p><p>Постройте суффиксный массив для заданной строки $$$s$$$.</p>"},"inSpecsHtml":{"en":"<div class=\"section-title\">Input</div><p>Input contains a single string $$$s$$$ of length $$$n$$$ ($$$1 \\le n \\le 400\\,000$$$). String consists of small english letters.</p>","ru":"<div class=\"section-title\">Входные данные</div><p>Первая строка входных данных содержит строку $$$s$$$ длины $$$n$$$ ($$$1 \\le n \\le 400\\,000$$$). Строка состоит из строчных букв латинского алфавита.</p>"},"outSpecsHtml":{"en":"<div class=\"section-title\">Output</div><p>Print $$$n + 1$$$ distinct integers, indices of first characters of suffixes of $$$s$$$, ordered in lexicographical order.</p>","ru":"<div class=\"section-title\">Выходные данные</div><p>Выведите $$$n + 1$$$ число — номера первых символов суффиксов строки $$$s$$$ в отсортированном порядке.</p>"},"noteHtml":{"en":null,"ru":null},"sampleTestcases":[{"id":1642049888358,"input":"ababba","output":"6 5 0 2 4 1 3 \n","result":{"id":1642049888358,"stdout":"6 5 0 2 4 1 3\n","stderr":"","exitcode":0,"signal":null,"time":1,"timeout":false}},{"id":1642049888359,"input":"aaaa\n","output":"4 3 2 1 0 \n","result":{"id":1642049888359,"stdout":"4 3 2 1 0\n","stderr":"","exitcode":0,"signal":null,"time":1,"timeout":false}},{"id":1642049888360,"input":"ppppplppp\n","output":"9 5 8 4 7 3 6 2 1 0 \n","result":{"id":1642049888360,"stdout":"9 5 8 4 7 3 6 2 1 0\n","stderr":"","exitcode":0,"signal":null,"time":1,"timeout":false}},{"id":1642049888361,"input":"nn\n","output":"2 1 0 \n","result":{"id":1642049888361,"stdout":"2 1 0\n","stderr":"","exitcode":0,"signal":null,"time":2,"timeout":false}}],"submitUrl":"https://codeforces.com/edu/course/2/lesson/2/2/practice/contest/269103/submit","language":"c++","langId":"54"}